@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_msdony(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.exp(tmp + 0.70) - wp.sin(v2 + 0.38)))
    tmp = wp.cos(v0)
    v1 = ((wp.sin(v1 + 0.75) * tmp) - wp.sin(0.85))
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.abs(v0 + 0.32) * wp.sin(tmp + 0.93)))
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.sin(v2 + 0.40)) + ((v1 + 0.36 / tmp + 0.12) / wp.sin(v0 + 0.44)))
    v1 = wp.exp(v1)
    v0 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
